description: This file defines a mock class 'SecureStorageServiceMock' for unit testing, which mocks the 'SecureStorageService::Service' interface from gRPC for secure storage operations. It includes mock methods for GetValue, UpdateValue, DeleteValue, DeleteAllValues, and SeedValue, facilitating testing of components dependent on this service.

classes.name: SecureStorageServiceMock
classes.description: A mock class for the SecureStorageService gRPC service, used in unit testing to simulate the behavior of the real service without performing actual operations.

methods.name: GetValue
methods.description: Mock method for retrieving a value from secure storage.

methods.name: UpdateValue
methods.description: Mock method for updating a value in secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteValue
methods.description: Mock method for deleting a specific value from secure storage.

methods.name: DeleteAllValues
methods.description: Mock method for deleting all values from secure storage.

methods.name: SeedValue
methods.description: Mock method for seeding a value into secure storage.
